00:40:51,210 --> 00:40:52,206
-Tian Yong.
-Yes!

541
00:40:52,290 --> 00:40:53,830
-You should tag along.
-Yes!

542
00:41:39,260 --> 00:41:41,270
Ms. Gu!

543
00:41:41,660 --> 00:41:43,590
-Village Chief.
-Director Mi.

544
00:41:43,740 --> 00:41:44,726
Have you found Ke Wei?

545
00:41:44,810 --> 00:41:45,690
Not yet.

546
00:41:45,820 --> 00:41:47,176
We tried to reach him through phone.

547
00:41:47,260 --> 00:41:50,446
A few days ago, there were still signals.
Now, we couldn't reach him at all.

548
00:41:50,530 --> 00:41:53,576
Before he left, did he say anything
or mention any place?

549
00:41:53,660 --> 00:41:55,470
My grandson is a good boy.

550
00:41:55,770 --> 00:41:57,806
He seldom talks.

551
00:41:57,890 --> 00:41:59,360
Did he behave abnormally?

552
00:41:59,770 --> 00:42:01,480
-No.
-He did.

553
00:42:01,700 --> 00:42:04,166
-He refused to sleep.
-It's like this.

554
00:42:04,250 --> 00:42:05,150
Lately,

555
00:42:05,620 --> 00:42:06,860
he's obsessed with computer games.

556
00:42:07,090 --> 00:42:08,080
Qian Rong,

557
00:42:08,300 --> 00:42:10,326
who is his mum,
paid him a visit a few days ago.

558
00:42:10,410 --> 00:42:11,736
She gave him a laptop.

559
00:42:11,820 --> 00:42:13,936
He's so excited.
He couldn't stop playing on the laptop.

560
00:42:14,020 --> 00:42:15,910
Where is the laptop?
Please show it to me.

561
00:42:23,460 --> 00:42:25,056
-Well...
-Well...

562
00:42:25,140 --> 00:42:26,900
This lady... Who is she?

563
00:42:27,250 --> 00:42:28,150
Report to the police.

564
00:42:30,770 --> 00:42:33,360
I've pasted the documents for you.

565
00:42:39,930 --> 00:42:40,840
Thank you.

566
00:42:42,650 --> 00:42:44,110
This is another set of documents.

567
00:42:44,500 --> 00:42:47,800
I need Professor Tang's help
to improvise it.

568
00:42:53,770 --> 00:42:55,446
Your main goal...

569
00:42:55,530 --> 00:42:57,800
in asking me to do all these
is not to build a factory in Dong'an.

570
00:42:58,730 --> 00:43:00,240
Your main goal...

571
00:43:00,690 --> 00:43:03,456
is to obtain project information
for the other companies, right?

572
00:43:03,540 --> 00:43:04,720
Is there any difference?

573
00:43:04,970 --> 00:43:06,446
I just want to focus on research.

574
00:43:06,530 --> 00:43:08,160
I don't want to be a commercial spy.

575
00:43:11,290 --> 00:43:14,910
Your salary for the month
has been transferred to your bank account.

576
00:43:15,458 --> 00:43:16,616
Where did you get the particulars?

577
00:43:16,700 --> 00:43:18,920
I have a way to obtain it.

578
00:43:41,650 --> 00:43:43,190
Professor Xia, good day.

579
00:43:43,340 --> 00:43:44,360
I'm Zhuo Ran.

580
00:43:44,540 --> 00:43:47,590
I saw on the news that an explosion
took place in Xia Chu's neighbourhood.

581
00:43:48,060 --> 00:43:49,280
Did she contact you?

582
00:43:50,010 --> 00:43:50,960
Is she okay?

583
00:43:57,100 --> 00:43:58,000
Lan Zi Yu!

584
00:43:58,420 --> 00:43:59,300
What's wrong?

585
00:43:59,500 --> 00:44:01,520
Is Xia Chu living at Cambridge Bay?

586
00:44:02,260 --> 00:44:03,326
You mean Ningjiang?

587
00:44:03,410 --> 00:44:04,630
Yes, her house in Ningjiang.

588
00:44:04,900 --> 00:44:06,000
Yes, what's wrong?

589
00:44:07,170 --> 00:44:09,710
Is she staying together
with Liang Mu Ze?

590
00:44:11,060 --> 00:44:12,870
She rented a room at his place.

591
00:44:13,410 --> 00:44:15,446
Furthermore, Liang Mu Ze
usually stays in the military camp.

592
00:44:15,530 --> 00:44:16,830
Why are you shouting?

593
00:44:18,490 --> 00:44:21,030
Just how many things
are you hiding from me?

594
00:44:59,770 --> 00:45:01,390
Will he die?

595
00:45:05,100 --> 00:45:07,030
I can't give you any confirmation on that,

596
00:45:09,330 --> 00:45:10,750
but please trust us.

597
00:45:11,610 --> 00:45:12,830
Xiao Xue!
